social_posts.post_text: I love my space dwarves so damn much. Converted this little fella so he looks like he dropped his gun in drunkenness. He’s gunna need to re roll a few dice to hit. Can’t wait to get to painting
I’m a little late because I was having a riot. Happy new year to you all, here are some pics as a sum up

Wanna watch two nerds beat each other up on a bridge? That’s what I thought. This flick is gunna be a fun one, @masonthegooding @itsmeganstott @dichenlachman and @tannerzagarino all go crazy in this. A wild ride filled with Army ranger executions all the way through, very fun stuff.
Happy Valentine’s Day to the gal who loves trumpets to the point of tears, my Calamity Jane, the mother of our furry baby. This one’s for you

I have so much pride for this project. Two years ago we embarked on The Duel, a group of friends with a mission to support each other and make films we ourselves would watch. The result is a project I’m immensely thankful for, giving me some of my best friends and memories on set in many years. As my debut executive producing a project, I couldn’t be more respectful of the hard work everyone put into this. Long story short, support your friends, make cool shit. #mammothff
Happy Beautiful Disaster release day! Go check ur local theaters baby! Very proud of all the hard work we did on this one, go support us!
Say hi to Travis ‘Mad Dog’ Maddox. There’s more than meets the eye when it comes to this bad boy 👀 Watch Beautiful Disaster now! 🔥

Been a long time Blizzard fanboy since forever. This last blizzcon was my first time attending in over 15 years, holy cow. After attending, @blizzard sent me this awesome new gift box to celebrate the release of @warcraftrumble excited to be able to finally get my Warcraft fix on set in between takes. The game is available for download on mobile now. This will come in handy…don’t tell the producers.
